- Researched Design & Potential Components
    - Power Stage
        - Buck Boost Converter: LTC3779
        - N-Channel Power MOSFETs (x4): Infineon BSC070N10NS5
        - Shielded Power Inductor: 10uH - 22uH
    - Communication
        - ESP32
            - Buck Converter (to Power): LM2596
    - Sensing & Feedback
        - Current Sensor: INA240
            - Shunt Resistor (that Current Sensor Reads): 5mÎ©
        - Precision Resistors (for Feedback Divider and DAC Injection)
    - Protection & Safety
        - Schottky Blocking Diode: MBR10100 (10A, 100V)
        - Automotive Blade Fuses: 10A
        - Transient Voltage Suppression Diodes
    - Passive Components 
        - Electrolytic Capacitors: 470uF, 100V (Input and Output bulk storage)
        - Ceramic Capacitors: 0.1uF & 10nF (for Bootstrap circuit and noise filtering)
- Began Simulating Design in Multisim
